    "121966198": {
      "title": "A class of deterministic self-affine processes",
      "abstract": "For each self-affine function with order strictly between zero and one, we construct a corresponding self-affine process of zero entropy. The Rudin-Shapiro process arising from the Rudin-Shapiro function is shown to be a zero entropy analogue of Brownian motion."
